00:00:03.080 --> 00:00:07.680
We're repeatedly given messages that we
live in sexually enlightened times.

00:00:07.680 --> 00:00:11.940
That we belong to a liberated age and
therefore the implication is that we

00:00:11.940 --> 00:00:16.590
ought by now, to be finding sex a
straightforward and un-troubling matter

00:00:16.590 --> 00:00:21.810
we're not after all Victorians or prudes.
The standard narrative of our release

00:00:21.810 --> 00:00:25.980
from past inhibitions go something like
this. For thousands of years

00:00:25.980 --> 00:00:29.760
right across the globe due to a devilish
combination of religious bigotry and

00:00:29.760 --> 00:00:33.870
pedantic social customs people were
afflicted by a ridiculous sense of

00:00:33.870 --> 00:00:36.120
confusion and guilt around sex.

00:00:36.120 --> 00:00:38.940
They thought their hands would fall off if
they masturbated.

00:00:39.180 --> 00:00:42.980
They believed they might be burned in a
vat of oil because they ogle [look at] someone's ankle.

00:00:43.260 --> 00:00:47.940
They had no clue about erections  or
clitorises. They will see that

00:00:47.940 --> 00:00:51.480
sometime between the first World War
and the launch of Sputnik 1,

00:00:51.480 --> 00:00:55.500
